author: Al Jazeera
title: US: Hundreds protest against coronavirus stay-at-home orders
description: Protests come as US deaths exceed 31,000; survey finds most Americans worry about virus restrictions lifted too soon.
content:
Hundreds of people have demonstrated in cities across the United States against coronavirus-related stay-at-home rules - with the explicit encouragement of President Donald Trump.
